text: The material relating to the responsibilities of the Technical Group (formerly ITG Compliance and Program Management) contained in IRM 4.86.10, Indian Tribal Governments Procedures, Compliance and Program Management (CPM) Responsibilities have been incorporated, where necessary, into revised IRM 4.86.5, Indian Tribal Governments Procedures, Conducting Indian Tribal Government Examinations.
